title: Tickets issued for 'Permit Parking' , Vancouver, 2004-2008
name: Tickets issued for 'Permit Parking' , Vancouver, 2004-2008
description: Total Tickets issued from 2004-2008 for 'Permit Parking' in Vancouver. This dataset shows the locations and number of tickets issued. Data was originally uploaded by the Vancouver Sun who received that data from a FOIA request. This data and other parking ticket data can be found at their Parking Ticket Database.
